rclone-azureblob-airgap (1.73.2-4) unstable; urgency=medium

  * debian/rules: bundle rclone-mount-example.conf in deb
    (usr/share/rclone-azureblob-airgap/examples/rclone-mount-example.conf).
  * build-deb.yml smoke-test: add assertion that all 8 fuse-debs are bundled
    (jammy+noble x amd64+arm64 x libfuse3-3+fuse3); fail if count != 8.
  * integration-test.yml: add non-interactive tests for all 7 auth methods:
    SAS URL (2), SP Secret (4), SP Certificate (5),
    MSI System-assigned (6a), MSI User-assigned (6b), env_auth (7).
  * verify-azureblob.sh, verify-mount.sh: fix install hint to show
    'sudo dpkg -i *.deb' as primary install method after deb era.

