rclone-azureblob-airgap (1.73.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * rclone v1.73.2 binary for amd64/arm64.
  * Offline FUSE3 packages for Ubuntu 22.04 (jammy) and 24.04 (noble).
  * Azure Blob Storage configuration templates for all auth methods.
  * systemd rclone-azureblob@.service instance template.
  * disable_instance_discovery support for Azure Private Link environments.
  * Interactive configure-azureblob.sh and verify-azureblob.sh scripts.

